<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
  <div>
    <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Bank Soal</div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Import Bank Soal</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Upload file Excel (.xlsx) atau CSV untuk menambahkan soal ke bank soal secara massal.</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium">💡 Rekomendasi: Gunakan template XLSX untuk kemudahan editing</p>
  </div>
  <a href="/teacher/question-bank" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-indigo-100 hover:from-indigo-100 hover:to-indigo-200 text-indigo-800 font-medium transition-all">← Kembali</a>
</div>

<div class="mt-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
  <!-- Card Langkah & Format -->
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 p-6 shadow-soft">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="text-2xl">📋</span>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900">Langkah & Format</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="text-sm text-blue-800 space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">1.</span>
        <span>Download template XLSX (Excel), lalu isi datanya dengan mudah.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">2.</span>
        <div>
          <div>Kolom wajib:</div>
          <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white text-blue-900 text-xs">question_text, points, correct, A, B, C, D, E</code>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">3.</span>
        <div>
          <div>Kolom opsional:</div>
          <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white text-blue-900 text-xs">image, difficulty, subject, chapter, tags</code>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">4.</span>
        <span>Kolom <code class="px-1 rounded bg-white">subject</code> isi kode/nama mapel. Jika kosong, pilih mapel default saat commit.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">5.</span>
        <div>
          <div>Kunci jawaban: isi huruf</div>
          <code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-white text-blue-900 text-xs">A / B / C / D / E</code>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 mt-0.5">6.</span>
        <span>Upload file XLSX/CSV yang sudah diisi, lalu klik Preview & Validasi.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2">
      <a href="/public/templates/question_import_template.xlsx"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-emerald-100 hover:from-emerald-100 hover:to-emerald-200 text-emerald-800 font-semibold text-sm text-center transition-all">
        📥 Download Template XLSX
      </a>
      <a href="/public/templates/import_template.csv"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-teal-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-teal-100 hover:from-teal-100 hover:to-teal-200 text-teal-800 font-semibold text-sm text-center transition-all">
        📥 Download Template CSV
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 flex gap-2">
      <a href="/teacher/question-bank"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-blue-700 text-white font-semibold text-sm text-center transition-all">
        📚 Lihat Bank Soal
      </a>
      <a href="/teacher/question-bank/upload-images"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-amber-600 hover:from-amber-600 hover:to-amber-700 text-white font-semibold text-sm text-center transition-all">
        🖼️ Upload Gambar Soal
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-100 border border-blue-200">
      <div class="text-xs text-blue-700">
        💡 <span class="font-semibold">Tip:</span> Template XLSX sudah dilengkapi dengan sheet Panduan. Buka di Microsoft Excel atau Google Sheets untuk hasil terbaik.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Card Upload Import -->
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-purple-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-6 shadow-soft">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="text-2xl">📤</span>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-900">Upload Import</h2>
    </div>

    <form action="/teacher/question-bank/import/preview" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="text-sm text-purple-700 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>📄</span>
          <span>File Excel/CSV</span>
        </label>
        <input type="file" name="file" accept=".xlsx,.csv,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet,text/csv" required
          class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl bg-white border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3 file:mr-4 file:py-2 file:px-4 file:rounded-lg file:border-0 file:bg-purple-100 file:text-purple-700 hover:file:bg-purple-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" />
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="text-sm text-purple-700 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>🖼️</span>
          <span>Gambar (opsional, multiple)</span>
        </label>
        <input type="file" name="images" accept="image/*" multiple
          class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl bg-white border-2 border-purple-200 px-4 py-3 file:mr-4 file:py-2 file:px-4 file:rounded-lg file:border-0 file:bg-purple-100 file:text-purple-700 hover:file:bg-purple-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500" />
        <div class="mt-2 p-2 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 text-xs text-purple-700">
          Nama file harus sama dengan kolom <code class="px-1 py-0.5 rounded bg-white">image</code> di template
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="w-full rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-purple-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02]">
        ✨ Preview & Validasi
      </button>
    </form>

    <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-xl bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200">
      <div class="text-xs text-amber-700">
        ⚡ <span class="font-semibold">Performa:</span> Jika file besar, pecah menjadi beberapa file (per 100–200 soal) untuk proses yang lebih stabil.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
